Last update: 26 december 2006.

This is a non-exhaustive guide to porting code from Kopete >= 0.11 (based on KDE3.x) to Kopete4 (based on KDE 4.x).

Libkopete changes
-----------------
*) kopetecommandhandler.h
   -CommandList is now a QMultiHash<QString, Command*>

*) kopeteproperties.h
   - Remplaced PortingDict, now a QMultiHash<QByteArray, PropertyData
   - Remplaced all const char * parameters with const QByteArray &

*) kopetexsl.h
   - Was removed in 0.12 version.

*) kopetemessage.h
   - asXML() no longer exist (removed in 0.12)

